  "title": "MEGMEM",
  "description": "MEGMEM is a magnetoencephalography (MEG) dataset acquired during a memory task designed to investigate neural mechanisms of episodic memory encoding and retrieval. The dataset contains raw MEG recordings from multiple subjects performing controlled memory experiments, providing a resource for studying oscillatory dynamics and neural correlates of memory processes.",
